  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Stone_Crows\" title=\"Stone Crows\"><img alt=\"Stone Crows.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/fb/Stone_Crows.svg/50px-Stone_Crows.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/fb/Stone_Crows.svg/75px-Stone_Crows.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/fb/Stone_Crows.svg/100px-Stone_Crows.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Dolf<br /><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> son of Holger</span></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Stone_Crows\" title=\"Stone Crows\"><img alt=\"Stone Crows.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/fb/Stone_Crows.svg/50px-Stone_Crows.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/fb/Stone_Crows.svg/75px-Stone_Crows.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/fb/Stone_Crows.svg/100px-Stone_Crows.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Stone_Crows\" title=\"Stone Crows\">Stone Crows</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Vale_mountain_clans\" title=\"Vale mountain clans\">Vale mountain clans</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Father</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Holger\" title=\"Holger\">Holger</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Issue</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Shagga\" title=\"Shagga\">Shagga</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i> (appendix)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i> (mentioned)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Dolf</b>, known as <b>Dolf son of Holger</b> because of <a href=\"/index.php/Holger\" title=\"Holger\">his father</a>, is the father of <a href=\"/index.php/Shagga\" title=\"Shagga\">Shagga son of Dolf</a> and a member of the <a href=\"/index.php/Stone_Crows\" title=\"Stone Crows\">Stone Crows</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> He taught Shagga everything he knew about warfare.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> It is unknown if Dolf is still alive.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Dolf&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ragot42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" titl